As a: Software Developer
I want: To obtain student data from the registrar
So that: Students do not have to manually input their academic history
Acceptance Criteria
● Is the data secure?
● Is the affected student informed of the data access request?
● Is there a way for the student to allow/deny data access?
● Is the method of transferring data from the registrar secure?
● Is the data password protected?
● Is the registrar office properly informed of the reason data is being requested?
● Is the registrar office confident in the security of any obtained data?
● Does the University permit the sharing of student data to another department?
